      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HE'S REGAL (7) is yet to miss the placings here in an excellent record which boasts five wins and two placings. Recorded a 2.25 lengths win (21.82) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Looks a leading chance on best. BENTLEY REX (2) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last six runs. Last start finished 2nd in a Grade 5 on March 20 over 411m at Casino behind Little Girl Gone beaten one length (23.54). Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Well-placed to take this out. WEATHER MAN RICK (1) is a smart beginner who has shown good improvement at his last two starts, the latest scoring at this track over 352m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Sure to measure up. DEVENISH DEVIL (8) is a last-start placegetter with solid claims again.",
